Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Chinese Pier Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Rasul
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 782
An Act Changing the Name of the Chinese Pier Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Rasul
Section 1. The name of the Chinese Pier Primary School in the Municipality of Jolo, Province of Sulu, is changed to Mababang Paaralan ng Rasul.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
